seo: Spring Cloud Config,目录遍历漏洞,CVE-2020-5405
summary: 检测Spring Cloud Config Server是否存在目录遍历漏洞（CVE-2020-5405），通过发送特定请求判断是否可以读取系统敏感文件。
summary_en: Detect whether the Spring Cloud Config Server has a directory traversal vulnerability (CVE-2020-5405) by sending specific requests to determine if system sensitive files can be read.
